            "text": "In this challenge lab, you will create a RESTful API using API Gateway that can handle dynamic path and query string parameters. The Lambda function will process the incoming parameters and respond with the necessary output. You'll get hands-on experience in combining API Gateway and Lambda, two powerful AWS services that simplify serverless application development."
