            "text": "You are developing a serverless API that receives data from a user via both path and query parameters. The user sends a request like GET /user/{id}?action=details, where {id} is a path parameter and action is a query string. Your task is to set up an API Gateway to capture these parameters and trigger an AWS Lambda function to process the request accordingly."
