            "text": "In this challenge, your Virtual Private Cloud (VPC) skills are put to the test. You'll be given a requirement and you have to reach it using your knowledge of Elastic Compute (EC2), Internet Gateway, Route Tables, Subnets and Transit gateway which will be used in this challenge. This Challenge will help you understand the real-time scenarios."
