            "text": "In this task, we are going to demonstrate the ability to purge a queue in Amazon SQS. Purging a queue means deleting all the messages in the queue. This task allows the user to understand the consequences of purging a queue and verify the successful deletion of messages. It also serves as a precautionary measure to ensure the queue is clean before performing further operations."
